{
  "stem": "13469.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we remember that, basically, it was not such a bad camp-- especially in retrospect what happened later.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For example, in-- in Belsen, I had to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The demarcation line in most camps seemed to be around 15, 16, and I was sometimes above it, sometimes below it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Westerbork, I had to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the work was not very arduous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think I had to pick potatoes in the fields, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I-- I had an arbeitskarte-- which I have here, amongst my collection of documents-- which clearly says, Paul Oppenheimer, arbeitskarter, Westerbork, barrack number 68.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the other side of it, in pencil, is written down all the days when I was excused from work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you will say-- see the date, and then it says, two days, cough-- or whatever it is, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Can't really decipher it all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you see quite clearly, the two days, three days, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I seem to have had lots of coughs and headaches and all sorts of illnesses, because when I've added it all up, I think it's something like 47 days I was excused from work, during the seven or eight months that we stayed in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that-- that is an interesting document which reminds me that I definitely did work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There's a lot of argument about what the age limit was in various camps, about who had to work, and who had not had to work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I certainly worked in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And obviously, my parents worked in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember what they did, but I don't believe that it was very arduous kind of work in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were, there was excellent medicine-- medical facilities.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
